To activate the Heater in the Living room on floor 1:
http://192.168.0.240:6666/home/floor1/LivingRoom/Heater?command=(string)on

To activate scene "TurnHeatersOff":
http://192.168.0.240:6666/home/floor1/LivingRoom/TurnHeatersOff
    ?command=(string)activate
